node.text:
A trusted insider at Epic Games has provided some info about upcoming Season and Chapter 3! The Cube will be returning at the end of Season 7 under the control of an unknown Queen character, which will lead directly into the story of Chapter 3. The insider also confirmed that the third chapter will include a complete redesign of the map, similar to how the current map is an upgrade from the Original Chapter 1 map. The location of The Seven will also be revealed in Chapter 3!
#Fortnite
(Concepts images by FNChiefAko/Twitter)
